OL,3,CEx-police officer jailed for more than
OL,4,C3 years for penalty points fraud
OL,6,FA former Sussex Police officer has
OL,7,Fbeen been sentenced to 38 months'
OL,8,Fimprisonment at Guildford Crown Court
OL,9,Fafter admitting a number of serious
OL,10,Foffences.
OL,12,FIt follows an investigation by the
OL,13,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,14,F(IOPC).
OL,16,FThe officer was also disqualified from
OL,17,Fdriving for two years, following his
OL,18,Frelease from prison.
