OL,3,CEx-police officer jailed for more than
OL,4,C3 years for penalty points fraud
OL,6,FSeren Sriganesh, aged 23, was formerly
OL,7,Fbased on the Brighton and Hove
OL,8,Fpolicing division.
OL,10,FHe pleaded guilty in January 2025 to
OL,11,Fconspiracy to pervert the course of
OL,12,Fjustice, conspiracy to commit fraud by
OL,13,Ffalse representation, fraud by failing
OL,14,Fto disclose information and unlawfully
OL,15,Fobtaining personal data.
OL,17,FThe charges relate to offending
OL,18,Fbetween September 2020 and February
OL,19,F2024.
