OL,3,CEx-police officer jailed for more than
OL,4,C3 years for penalty points fraud
OL,6,FThe former officer falsely nominated
OL,7,Fhis parents as responsible for three
OL,8,Fseparate driving offences and
OL,9,Funlawfully accessed police systems to
OL,10,Fview details of one of these offences.
OL,12,FSriganesh also failed to declare he
OL,13,Fhad six or more penalty points on his
OL,14,Flicence prior to joining the force in
OL,15,FJune 2023 and did not disclose these
OL,16,Fpoints to his motor insurers.
OL,18,FIOPC director Emily Barry said: "The
OL,19,Fevidence gathered in this case was
OL,20,Foverwhelming and undoubtedly led to Mr
OL,21,FSriganesh's guilty plea.
