OL,3,CEx-police officer jailed for more than
OL,4,C3 years for penalty points fraud
OL,6,F"I would like to pay tribute to the
OL,7,Fofficers from Sussex Police anti-
OL,8,Fcorruption unit who worked
OL,9,Fmeticulously to investigate this
OL,10,Fmatter.
OL,12,F"The public have a right to expect
OL,13,Fpolice officers to act with honesty
OL,14,Fand integrity, and it is a gross
OL,15,Fbreach of trust when they break the
OL,16,Flaw.
