OL,6,F"Mr Sriganesh flagrantly and
OL,7,Frepeatedly broke the law for his own
OL,8,Fpersonal gain and today he has faced
OL,9,Fthe very serious consequences of his
OL,10,Factions."
OL,12,FSeren Sriganesh resigned from Sussex
OL,13,FPolice in October 2024.
